OL,3,CHundreds of farmers launch legal
OL,4,Caction against company planning pylon
OL,5,Chighways
OL,7,FHundreds of Welsh farmers and
OL,8,Flandowners have launched High Court
OL,9,Flegal action against a green energy
OL,10,Fcompany planning to build pylons
OL,11,Facross Wales.
OL,13,FMore than 300 people have accused
OL,14,FGreen GEN Cymru of an "unlawful" abuse
OL,15,Fof power to "force" access onto
OL,16,Fprivate land, with some expressing
OL,17,Fthey feel their "homes are being
OL,18,Finvaded".
