OL,4,Caction against company planning pylon
OL,5,Chighways
OL,7,FAccording to court documents, agents
OL,8,Facting on behalf of the company are
OL,9,Faccused of behaving in a "coercive"
OL,10,Fand careless manner, "without regard
OL,11,Ffor environmental protections or
OL,12,Fcommunity wellbeing".
OL,14,FThe farmers and landowners claim that
OL,15,Fthe agents tried to force their way
OL,16,Fonto land to conduct surveys for pylon
OL,17,Fhighways spanning more than 200km in
OL,18,Frural Wales.
