OL,4,Caction against company planning pylon
OL,5,Chighways
OL,7,FThe proposed scheme will see three
OL,8,Fpylon routes run through the counties
OL,9,Fof Powys, Ceredigion and
OL,10,FCarmarthenshire, leading to the
OL,11,FCambrian Mountains.
OL,13,FFarmers and local residents have long
OL,14,Fopposed the proposed overhead pylon
OL,15,Froutes, instead calling for the cables
OL,16,Fto be placed underground to protect
OL,17,Fthe landscape and environment.
