OL,7,FITV Cymru Wales previously spoke to
OL,8,Fresidents across Powys who were
OL,9,F"dumbfounded" by the plans to erect
OL,10,Flarge pylons across rural land. Locals
OL,11,Fdescribed the proposals as
OL,12,F"industrialising" the Welsh
OL,13,Fcountryside, with fears that the
OL,14,Ftowering metal structures would scar
OL,15,Fsome of the "most scenic areas".
