OL,7,FEnergy companies argue that such
OL,8,Finfrastructure is vital to meeting the
OL,9,FUK's renewable energy goals and
OL,10,Fensuring that electricity generated by
OL,11,Fnew wind farms can reach the national
OL,12,Fgrid.
OL,14,FThe legal claim, filed by the law firm
OL,15,FNew South Law, argues that the energy
OL,16,Ffirm is acting beyond its powers as an
OL,17,Facquiring authority ` a body given
OL,18,Flegal power to compulsorily acquire
OL,19,Fland for public projects.
