OL,5,Chighways
OL,7,FNatalie Barstow, the named claimant
OL,8,Fand founder of Justice for Wales,
OL,9,Fwhich calls for fairness and lawful
OL,10,Fprocesses in the planning and delivery
OL,11,Fof major energy projects, said: "We
OL,12,Fhave been left no choice but to seek
OL,13,Flegal action through the High Court as
OL,14,Fa result of this bullying campaign by
OL,15,FGreen GEN Cymru.
OL,17,F"We've had hundreds of reports from
OL,18,Fpeople feeling as if their homes are
OL,19,Fbeing invaded ` many feel powerless,
OL,20,Foutnumbered, and fearful of being
OL,21,Farrested or prosecuted.
