OL,7,FMary Smith, a lawyer at New South Law,
OL,8,Fsaid: "This case raises fundamental
OL,9,Fquestions about accountability in the
OL,10,FUK's renewable energy transition and
OL,11,Fhow industry behaviour is threatening
OL,12,Fthe environment and communities' human
OL,13,Frights."
OL,15,FShe added: "Having the status of an
OL,16,Facquiring authority carries a
OL,17,Fresponsibility to behave lawfully and
OL,18,Fto treat the public reasonably and
OL,19,Ffairly.
